This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and summarization. It could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as it involves extracting relevant information from news articles. Additionally, it could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it involves machine learning techniques for summarization. It may also be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training models for summarization. Finally, it could be relevant to cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it deals with the impact of technology on society through the analysis of news articles.
